{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Abolish Election Deposits.",
        "additional_details": "Election deposits are virtually a \u2018tax\u2019 on democracy. The deposits required to run for election by the public should be scrapped in order to enable a wider range of candidates to stand and open up the Democratic process of Elections.",
        "background": "We ask the Government to abolish election deposits, it does not seem reasonable to have a barrier to standing for election that depends on someone\u2019s financial means. We do not think the ability to pay a specified fee is a relevant or appropriate criterion for determining access to the ballot paper.",
